OWNERS ARE RELOCATING!! REDUCED PRICE $7K IN LESS THAN 60 DAYS!! WILL LOOK AT OFFERS!! This Perry Construction 4 bedroom plus 3 full baths is perfect fit with all bedrooms on the lower level with 2 full baths and upstairs has a full bath with large play/projector (projector setup off the wall and surround audio system included) . All counter tops are draped in granite with large bull nose corners. The living area is an open concept which can be overlooked by breakfast nook and kitchen with dividing bar sitting area. The tall ceilings of this home give it a larger than 2,885 feeling and the flooring throughout the home compliments the home well with dark laminate mix large ceramic tile in hall areas, kitchen, & bathrooms. ADDITIONAL: LESS than 2 year old AC unit & insulated roofing.  
Home will temporarily removed from the market on Dec. 15, 2015.
